---------------------------------------------------

        1.0. Project Introduction.

---------------------------------------------------

The purpose of this project is to showcase my PHP, SQL and documentation skills while showcasing a simple button game, try to beat the highscore!

---------------------------------------------------

        2.0. Installation / Prerequisites.

---------------------------------------------------

Prerequisite

•  Xammp installed.
•  SQL installed.
•  PHP installed.

Installation

•  Download code into your workspace
•  Make sure code folder is placed into XAMMP > HTDOC folder set up to run on localhost.

